    'description' => 'Full web research pipeline: fetch a URL via http_fetch, extract readable text via html_to_text, and optionally summarize the content via text_summarizer. Returns structured data: title, readable text, links, summary. Composes three distinct tool domains (network, HTML parsing, NLP) into one operation. Never throws — all errors returned as structured data.',
    'parameters' => 
